{"tid":1332354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會秘書處：使用者周日勿返回大樓","createTime":"2019-07-19T09:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T09:53:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22d5e1923ef3854ebb4308288575a2c89f9e5f7d","tid":1332354,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"民陣周日(21日)再度發起反修例遊行，並於今日收到警方不反對通知書，遊行原定以中環遮打道終審法院為終點，但警方以公共秩序安全為由，限制遊行終點必須設於灣仔盧押道與莊士敦道交界。<br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處向議員發出公告稱，經評估風險後，<span style=\"color: red;\">秘書處只會安排保安人員於7月21日在大樓提供有限度服務。</span><br />\n<br />\n為確保安全，<span style=\"color: red;\">秘書處呼籲所有大樓使用者不要在當天返回大樓</span>。此外，由於大樓及停車場的出入口可能會被阻塞，議員應避免駕車前往大樓，以免車輛無法進出停車場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2195801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2195801%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=c5e08c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2195801/</a>"},{"pid":"db7783ca98e3c20d38923bebba9a8fad333b9e44","tid":1332354,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2b2864df5372f08ca64e67af41b499cc836b0153","tid":1332354,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"又封立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b2fe8193f5ab0e8541944f035a13f9b5555550","tid":1332354,"uid":14486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"即係戒嚴"},{"pid":"f7f445a510d9a4751d41f0ed212355260d058170","tid":1332354,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm